This is the "experimental" part of my Bachelor's Thesis.

Dependencies:

node.js
    http://github.com/creationix/nvm or for exmample MacPorts
npm
    http://github.com/isaacs/npm
DNode
    npm install dnode
Vows
    npm install vows

JSBuild
    http://github.com/azer/jsbuild
Google Closure Linter
    http://code.google.com/closure/utilities/docs/linter_howto.html
Google Closure Compiler
    http://code.google.com/closure/compiler/docs/gettingstarted_app.html


I try to remove the hardcoded paths in the future.

